reviewText: If you've been watching the previous box sets like I have, then you've got to get this one. The first disc is simply just untold stories from the past, the second disc is much more interesting. Many more reanimated Shinobi battles & at the end Kabuto summons someone very special, anyone you has played the recent games for this series knows you I mean & anyone who hasn't played the games should definitely watch this epic moment.
Very good !!!

Love Naruto and have all box sets but I stopped buying them around the start of the 3rd great ninja war. No more for me until they are release in blue-ray .... unexceptionably. It's 2016.

It's not bad to watch the show, especially waiting for 4 months of waiting, disappointing, apoorling and unprofessional from viz media studios and English voice casters. I just hope 2016 doesn't become another bad year like 2015 occurred. Next Naruto shippuden dvd set 26 323-335 will be out on April 5th 2016. My guess is that next dvd cover 26 will be Naruto Uzumaki in his tailed beast mode.

Set 25 continues the fourth great ninja war with episodes 310 to 322. Also features a special episode prologue of road to ninja. Which I have yet to watch, waiting to see the special episode first. =) In all seriousness a fantastic upcoming set to add to your Naruto anime collection!

Episode 322 Amazing

The episode 322 justified the price of  the entire set. The level of animation and quality of fight choreography is by far the best in shippuden so far (DUB). I would even go as far as even in the movie sets, they have never achieved such fight sequences quality. You literately have to watch this episode more than once to catch up with all actions, specially Madara's fighting skills. There is not a lot of chattering in this episode and by the end you feel exhuasted by the amount of furious and fast action. The animation quality has also increased incredibly, you see how much the animators have spent time capturing the emotions of the fighters. Sadly I know there is a little chance I see another episode like this since the cost must have been quite high for this episode
